instruction: Generate a mnemonic for the numbers 1 - 10
output:
One elephant slipped through the doorway. 
Two little ducks quacked quietly. 
Three brown bears crossed the road. 
Four kittens meowed majestically. 
Five little monkeys jumped on the bed. 
Six puppies barked loudly. 
Seven flowers bloomed in the garden. 
Eight honeybees buzzed around. 
Nine frogs croaked in the night. 
Ten turtles waddled away.
